These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-1::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: card-games, collecting
House: palace, townhouse
1. the palace house is in an even position##4
2. the townhouse house is the person who's hobby is collecting##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |
| Hobby   | collecting | card-games |
| House     | townhouse    | palace   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-2::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: may, august
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: sailing, weightlifting
1. the person who's sport is sailing is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the person who's birthday is in may##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |
| Birthday   | august | may        |
| Sport      | sailing  | weightlifting |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-3::.
There 2 different types of food: lemon, grapes
There are 2 different nationalities: canadian, turkish
1. the canadian is in an odd position##4
2. the person eating grapes is on the left of the person eating lemon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |
| Food   | grapes    | lemon |
| Nationality   | canadian | turkish |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-4::.
2 different pets are kept: snake, bird
There 2 different types of food: broccoli, mango
1. the owner of the bird is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
2. the person eating mango is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2     |
| Pet   | snake      | bird |
| Food       | broccoli | mango    |

 #################################

 
