.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-10::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  fisherman, dancer
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: country, folk
1. the fan of folk is the dancer##1
2. the fan of country is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |     2     |
| Job          | dancer | fisherman |
| Music-Genre   | folk | country   |

