.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-11::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: sudoku, video-games
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: skiing, volleyball
1. the person who's hobby is video-games is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |
| Hobby   | video-games | sudoku   |
| Sport         | skiing | volleyball |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-12::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: disco, jazz
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: thriller, disaster
1. the person watching thriller movies is the fan of disco##1
2. the person watching disaster movies is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |
| Music-Genre   | jazz       | disco   |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster | thriller |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-13::.
