The people prefer 2 different types of sport: snowboarding, water-polo
1. the person who growsazalea is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
2. the person who growsazalea is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2      |
| Flower   | tulip | azalea      |
| Sport         | snowboarding | water-polo |

