.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-17::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, almond-milk
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: biathlon, weightlifting
1. the person who's sport is biathlon is in an even position##4
2. the person drinking almond-milk is the person who's sport is weightlifting##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |      2      |
| Beverage     | almond-milk    | hot-chocolate |
| Sport   | weightlifting | biathlon    |

